366
00:19:58,310 --> 00:19:59,710
Stop joking.

367
00:19:59,710 --> 00:20:00,990
I’m so worried now.

368
00:20:03,710 --> 00:20:04,670
I hardly know

369
00:20:04,670 --> 00:20:07,390
