489
00:25:41,910 --> 00:25:42,630
What do you mean?

490
00:25:43,150 --> 00:25:44,470
Mr. Luo means

491
00:25:44,630 --> 00:25:45,830
it would be tiring on the way.

492
00:25:46,110 --> 00:25:48,470
